OL,3,CNottingham Forest and football world
OL,4,Cpay tribute to John Robertson
OL,6,FFootball clubs, fans and former
OL,7,Fplayers have been paying tribute to
OL,8,FJohn Robertson, widely regarded as
OL,9,FNottingham Forest's 'greatest ever'
OL,10,Fplayer, following his death at the age
OL,11,Fof 72.
OL,13,FRobertson was a key figure in Brian
OL,14,FClough's historic side that won the
OL,15,FFirst Division title in 1978 and
OL,16,Fbacktoback European Cups in 1979 and
OL,17,F1980.
