OL,3,CNottingham Forest and football world
OL,4,Cpay tribute to John Robertson
OL,6,FHe provided the decisive assist for
OL,7,FTrevor Francis in the 1979 European
OL,8,FCup final and scored the winning goal
OL,9,Fin the 1980 final at the Bernabeu.
OL,11,FThe Lanarkshireborn winger, who made
OL,12,Fover 500 appearances for Forest with
OL,13,F95 goals, also represented Scotland 28
OL,14,Ftimes and featured at two World Cups
OL,15,Fbefore finishing his playing career
OL,16,Fwith a spell at Derby County.
