OL,3,CNottingham Forest and football world
OL,4,Cpay tribute to John Robertson
OL,6,FForest issued a heartfelt statement,
OL,7,Fsaying: "We are heartbroken to
OL,8,Fannounce the passing of Nottingham
OL,9,FForest legend and dear friend, John
OL,10,FRobertson.
OL,12,F"A true great of our club and a double
OL,13,FEuropean Cup winner, John's unrivalled
OL,14,Ftalent, humility and unwavering
OL,15,Fdevotion to Nottingham Forest will
OL,16,Fnever ever be forgotten.
OL,18,F"Our thoughts are with John's family,
OL,19,Ffriends and all who loved him.
OL,21,F"Rest in Peace, Robbo... Our greatest."
