OL,4,Cpay tribute to John Robertson
OL,6,FFormer teammate Peter Shilton
OL,7,Fdescribed Robertson as "our NFFC
OL,8,Fmiracle man", while exForest
OL,9,Fmidfielder Andy Reid called him the
OL,10,Fbest player ever to wear the garibaldi
OL,11,Fshirt and "an incredible human being".
OL,13,FRobertson later forged a respected
OL,14,Fcoaching career, working as assistant
OL,15,Fto Martin O'Neill at clubs including
OL,16,FCeltic, Leicester City and Aston
OL,17,FVilla. Across the game, tributes
OL,18,Fhighlighted not just his skill but his
OL,19,Fcharacter.
