OL,4,Cpay tribute to John Robertson
OL,6,FAston Villa confirmed they were
OL,7,F"deeply saddened" by his passing,
OL,8,Fremembering Robertson for his
OL,9,Fcontribution as assistant manager
OL,10,Funder O'Neill.
OL,12,FAt Leicester City, where he also
OL,13,Fworked as part of O'Neill's backroom
OL,14,Fteam, former Forest and Leicester
OL,15,Fforward Stan Collymore paid emotional
OL,16,Ftribute on social media, calling
OL,17,FRobertson "one of the loveliest,
OL,18,Fkindest hearted humans" he'd met and
OL,19,Fpraising his influence both on and off
OL,20,Fthe pitch.
