OL,3,CNottingham Forest and football world
OL,4,Cpay tribute to John Robertson
OL,6,F"His skill and vision made him one of
OL,7,Fthe game's finest, and his legacy will
OL,8,Flive on. Rest in peace, John.
OL,10,F"Thank you for the memories and for
OL,11,Finspiring generations of football
OL,12,Flovers."
